{"tid":1309964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【預先戒備】傳中銀要求分行員工明天全體上班","createTime":"2019-07-12T12:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T22:58:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8763c9d834af1bf5d1d5f65e0bebf6d4fcf14454","tid":1309964,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"反對《逃犯條例》修訂民情未息，繼早前有網民呼籲取消中資銀行戶口，取出存款後，再有網民號召明日發動「全民撳錢」行動。有中銀香港(2388)內部人士向本報表示，中銀香港要求全港分行前線員工明日全部上班，對前線員工的解釋，是為預備客戶申請銀色債券而增加人手(銀債申請日期為7月10日至18日)。但有內部人士分析，增加人手相信是要預防事故發生，有需要時調動人手支援高危地區的分行。<br />\n<br />\n有消息又指，中銀評估過響應行動的市民，本身在中銀的存款也不會太多，相信對銀行資金影響很有限。<br />\n<br />\n本報向中銀方面查詢，惟暫時未見回覆。"},{"pid":"59f42d3ed2aff2175e7f5f16162b8e6ae31c15c4","tid":1309964,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdda2195a4f7dae737a9454349ec76688f3afccc","tid":1309964,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1c46dc847eface8d3bec3726192128264af3df","tid":1309964,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdda2195a4f7dae737a9454349ec76688f3afccc","tid":1309964,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"點睇"},{"pid":"31b33a0cd2659a2bb7afe28ef7b5153efe5b9910","tid":1309964,"uid":103759,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5c1c46dc847eface8d3bec372619212826